data.title: Spot Bitcoin ETFs Pull In $129M, Ethereum ETFs Add $78M as Prices Hold Strong
data.description: Spot Bitcoin exchange-traded funds (ETFs) saw $129 million in net inflows on November 25, while Ether spot ETFs added another $78 million amid renewed demand across major issuers.
